@page "/"

<h3>This demo shows RPC calls from server to client. </h3>

<p>Each time client starts, it receives from server maximum value to find prime numbers</p>
<li>Calculates them locally and send result back to server.</li>
<li>Another client is getting those primes as they come and makes calculation at the same time to find next range of prime numbers</li>
<hr>
<p><i>The top 5 prime numbers found: </i></p>
<div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-content-start">

    @foreach (var prime in _primeNumbers.OrderByDescending(x => x).Take(5))
    {
        <div class="p-2 border">@prime</div>
    }
</div>
